  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to examine the effectiveness of 3 behavioral weight loss
      programs- Weight Watchers, university-based behavioral weight loss treatment, and a combined
      approach which includes university-based treatment followed by Weight Watchers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
